Subject: Yang-Mills Construction Route Checklist

Description: Project-local tool for checking whether a Yang-Mills mass-gap idea advances the regularized-to-continuum construction, Osterwalder-Schrader reconstruction, nontriviality, or spectral-gap proof route.

& [YangMillsConstructionRouteChecklist] is a math inquiry tool
  + [tool_uuid] is 0f9b4256-5368-43f6-8f65-f4e7a648582c
  + [problem] is Yang-Mills Existence and Mass Gap
  + [created_at] is 2026-06-26
  + [trigger_record] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\events\proof_inquiry\2026-06-26_yang_mills_deep_research_construction_route_001.sop
  + [role] is classify proposed mechanisms by construction route stage and expose missing continuum or gap locks
  + [not_role] is proving Yang-Mills, validating unaccepted claimed solutions, or replacing proof with physical intuition

& [ChecklistStages] is the required route
  + [stage_001_regularized_model] is a precise finite-cutoff, finite-volume, lattice, or other regularized Yang-Mills model is defined
  + [stage_002_uniform_estimates] is estimates survive cutoff removal and infinite-volume limits
  + [stage_003_continuum_limit] is continuum Euclidean measure or Schwinger functions are constructed
  + [stage_004_os_properties] is reflection positivity, Euclidean invariance, symmetry, regularity, and clustering properties are proved as needed
  + [stage_005_reconstruction] is Hilbert space, Hamiltonian, fields or gauge-invariant observables, and Wightman-type theory are reconstructed
  + [stage_006_gauge_and_nontriviality] is gauge-invariant content and nontrivial interacting character are established
  + [stage_007_gap_mechanism] is exponential correlation decay or direct spectral separation is proved
  + [stage_008_gap_transfer] is the gap survives reconstruction as positive Hamiltonian spectral gap above vacuum

& [Classification] is how a proposed mechanism is routed
  + [construction_relevant] is advances stages 001 through 006 with proof obligations stated
  + [gap_relevant] is advances stages 007 through 008 with continuum/reconstruction dependence stated
  + [heuristic_relevant] is suggests confinement, localization, or massive excitation without route-stage proof
  + [outside] is symbolic or simulation-only material with no route-stage contact

  = must: distinguish finite lattice from continuum
  = must: distinguish correlation decay evidence from reconstructed spectral gap
  = must: distinguish gauge fixing from gauge-invariant physical content
  = must: classify nontriviality separately from existence
  - never: call a gap proved before the continuum theory and Hamiltonian route are in place

(yang_mills_construction_route_checklist) :candidate_mechanism: /regularization, uniform estimates, OS reconstruction, nontriviality, gap transfer/ |lattice-or-metaphor-overclaim|
  + [inside] is route-stage classification and missing-lock detection
  + [boundary] is a mechanism can be promising while still failing the Millennium proof route
  |outside| sealed curvature as proof, finite-lattice gap as continuum proof, and physical confinement intuition as axiomatic construction
